(1) The Committee shall establish sub-committees for the purpose of performing its functions under this Act and in particular shall establish a— (a) Financial Sub- Committee ; (b) Legal and Administrative Sub- Committee ; (c) Social and Personnel Sub- Committee ; (d) Development and Planning Sub- Committee ; (e) Marketing Sub- Committee ; (f) Technical and Production Sub- Committee ; and (g) Security and Safety Sub- Committee .
